==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔːrəs|-ɔːrəs]]

===Adjective===
'''chlorous'''

#{{chemistry}} Of a [[compound]], containing [[chlorine]] with a lower [[oxidation number]] than equivalent [[chloric]] compounds; especially having an oxidation number of 3.

====Derived terms====
*[[chlorous acid]]
*[[chlorous anhydride]]
*[[chlorous oxide]]
*[[chlorous pole]]
*[[hypochlorous]]

====Related terms====
*[[chloric]]

